{"tid":51998,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"AirPods悲劇終於發生！日本網民購買三日後跌落路軌","createTime":"2016-12-23T16:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T09:03:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f956fee0f813ea6adea15dbfc3b8cad2159b515","tid":51998,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"Apple 最新款的無線藍牙耳筒AirPods 近日已陸續出貨，而日本方面首批買家就於本週一（12 月 19 日）入手。雖然 Tim Cook 之前曾強調 AirPods 戴起上來好穩陣，點跳點揈都不容易甩出來，但意外卻總會發生，比如有日本網民用了幾日，就不小心將 AirPods 整跌落路軌。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說該位名為 okaymac（オーケーマック）的日本網民，本週一 AirPods 正式發售時就已即時入手，其後當然就立即不斷使用，並分享了一些用後感想。不過去到本週三（12 月 21 日），亦即是 AirPods 入手三日後就發生悲劇了，據 okaymac 描述當日吃完晚飯後，他就如常坐電車離開，不過當他落車之後，配戴中的 AirPods 卻不幸地跌落路軌，而他即刻嚇到心都離一離。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://css.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/003-69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcss.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F003-69.jpg&h=f2486772&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://css.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/004-42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcss.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F004-42.jpg&h=a8ef4621&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/005-17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F005-17.jpg&h=8f52e15f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd759689454948a64f83221a3f497580f6a87237","tid":51998,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"笑左"},{"pid":"284f1d974aa311d6616e2f986075c43cf645f795","tid":51998,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"不過不幸中之大幸是 AirPods 並非跌正在車轆接觸的路軌面上，而只是在路軌的旁邊，即表示它仍有獲救機會。接著 okaymac 通知車站職員，最後在另一班電車駛開之後，職員就用膠紙的長棒將 AirPods 黐上來，結果這隻新耳筒才能倖免於難。至於為何會發生意外，okaymac 表示應該是由於他除下頸上的職員證時，頸繩意外地勾到 AirPods 突出來的尾部，於是 AirPods 才會以拋物線跌落路軌，所以如大家平時有戴頸鍊或職員證，那麼使用 AirPods 就要更加小心了。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://js1.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/006-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjs1.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F006-8.jpg&h=12358189&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec747d51364dee9efbc9b575e4b378057a513d23","tid":51998,"uid":9989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"通地執不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b1aa9ac49d08331c6e3763232cff04a9f359b7","tid":51998,"uid":21,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"多謝六百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19cb70943e91bcf40467751a1e80aede77c3108","tid":51998,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:52:33.000Z","msg":"第日港鐵站大把有得執，人迫啲跌咗踢幾踢想執返都難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23e4b9b9c3513c4351cf3dbf8bfda5ddd6b929a","tid":51998,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T23:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fe624abbf93ead0c7aca9a9c6049068f4213df","tid":51998,"uid":46560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:00:22.000Z","msg":"成班on9，佢係條帶勾到先跌咋"},{"pid":"1b2769ff50f6370003a34c05857d8a1ef389d918","tid":51998,"uid":24833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:08:03.000Z","msg":"執到又點呢，你都無個盒點pair，兩個智障連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dc81be58cbd72ca8ba342f99675662bec7f213","tid":51998,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:13:06.000Z","msg":"可以加番條耳機繩<br />\n就好似當年怕跌手機，個個都整條手機繩"},{"pid":"fcff0f7d6799c0f6011a9fb67465fc0de7c25424","tid":51998,"uid":48899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201